title: Lunchbox Gives Baby Box Post-Surgery Update + Why One City Can’t Watch Bobby Dance Next Week

Lunchbox gives an update on how Baby Box is doing after hernia surgery. One city won’t be able to watch Bobby dance Monday night. Also, Amy gives and update on her dad and the Pistol Annies stop by.
